</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>A complex vector into which the eigen values are set. Given as a pointer. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>evec</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>A complex Matrix into which the eigen vectors are set. Given as a pointer.  </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
